Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我改好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:12.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然速度也很惊人  但是真正让我惊讶的是内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,模糊不清的地方都进行了改善
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:19.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无论何处都没有冲突  全文条理清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这份做得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:21.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,快去交给部长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没通过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是对方谈到了公司的收支情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这些我们技术人员完全不懂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以她根本无法招架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我对意志消沉的她说了这样一句话
