Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明收下了好处  艾尔玛还是没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:11.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她组建了工会  组织会议让大家讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拼尽全力呼吁改善工作环境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,令人意外的是  托尔居然在帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毕竟顺利的话  以后小林就能早点回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你可不要拖我的后腿啊  艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敌对势力为了共同利益而一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都感觉或许能成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是  董事实在是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:43.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,运用道理和诡辩  将这些提议全部驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可恶  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:52.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样不是就赶不上去排车站前的限定点心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,理由居然是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,奇迹般地完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赶上了限定点心的最后一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给我三个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给我两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给我两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一个就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃着好吃的点心度过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们想去野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,出远门不能没有大人陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她好像说了休息日也要上班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那托尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她给你写了信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:54.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜看了求生电视节目之后  突然很想去山里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我今天要去女仆咖啡厅帮忙所以不能陪她去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以麻烦你带她们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我姑且还是信任你的  别让我失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔居然说她信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然有些居高临下的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吧  我同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我带你们去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了  康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就在这里搭帐篷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太是在去艾尔玛大人家里时在途中碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就叫他一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后呢  要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们租了钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,康娜  我们要钓什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.02,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,亚马逊森蚺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,钓鱼啊  不禁让人想起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:51.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也被钓过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有没有什么办法能快点钓到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,用手抓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再往那边一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那边有鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为我也喜欢往去那种地方钻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你也喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖喱和饭也煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看来带孩子也没有很难嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖喱真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  这虫子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是毒虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也去放松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我最近在研究能不能从龙脉里汲取魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,山上有很强大的龙脉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男孩子都喜欢这种设定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,孩子们都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微不注意就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这点事都做不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对了  我会千里眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样就能马上找到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有人想从远处偷窥我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一定是露科亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她偶尔就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有注意防范的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男孩子还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么  捕捉不到他们的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就不该找你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能会找不到回去的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为只是沿着龙脉走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原路返回就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以说男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们来之前好像没跟艾尔玛姐姐打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赶快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有没有听到什么吼叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能是这附近有熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛姐姐不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因为我们随意走动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她生我们的气就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能是去找我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可恶  究竟去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:12:59.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跪拜求饶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没点用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:01.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,干啥啥不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好  你很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.13,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,但还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始  心中的托尔就一直在痛骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.84,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,又蠢又搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你好  我在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有见到过几个小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混蛋  你想被吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可恶  你们一个两个都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:31.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,会去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:39.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:41.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之前在河边看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可让我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:13:59.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么  是花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是为了艾尔玛大人摘的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,送给你所以原谅我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同学那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好甜  原谅你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真好哄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是我在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天的花蜜我也吃得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,花蜜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我采的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么样  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.06,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,什么样的花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这下你可不能觉得我可怜可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.10,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,大花  而且很香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可没这么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给你的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别蹬鼻子上脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天气变热了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为到夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.98,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}由于各种原因（艾尔玛三昧）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我向来不会答应调和势力的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但这种暴力解决问题的方式我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这次看在你的份上  助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天我们采访会移动的动物园ZOO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最有名的居然是传闻中的长颈鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们来请教宫本园长几个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛邀请托尔出来还真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,「最近身体变迟钝了陪我出来活动活动筋骨」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:20.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,更加少见的是托尔居然就这么答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:24.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,两人之间的隔阂终于要消解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,态度也都软化了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定会以此为契机…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你太天真了  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你觉得她为什么会叫我们一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:44.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么时候停下来  由你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身体哪里迟钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,事到如今还想决出个胜负来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你能回到原来的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还没死心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你还是很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在蛊惑人心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她嘴上说着主张调和  引导人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:13.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那不过是因为她所处的立场罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她也曾被人利用  遭人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:20.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在心底里还是会与人类保持一定距离的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以现在依然怀疑托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:28.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我又没想干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,压根没想过把人类怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过是保持了一定的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以你就开心地在女仆咖啡厅和人类一起干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明以前态度上对人类毫不信任  不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在却完全转变过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在原来的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还不是把为人类所崇拜的我当傻子看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你只是被供奉了起来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,实际上你并没接触他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而一脸开心的样子过于滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.83,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(957.333,919.333)\bord2\1a&H73&\c&H000000&\t(1000,1250,\bord0)\t(1249,1250\c&H000000&\1a&H00&)\t(1000,1521,\blur10)}「把他们当作蚂蚁看才对」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.83,Kobayashi S2 - Next,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(957.333,919.333)\bord0\t(1249,1250,)\t(1000,1521,\be20)}「把他们当作蚂蚁看才对」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但你现在吃的不再是献上的供品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经可以自己买吃的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是那时的饭菜更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这才让人无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,更好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你还不赶紧滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吃是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而你却不知所踪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那时听说你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊  然后好不容易找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对我这么冷淡却和人类相谈甚欢
